			<figure class="dfe-image dfe-image__large"><div class="image-container calculated-ratio-16-9 aspect-ratio-16-9"><img src="/han/media/images/2025/03/HAN-Health-Advisory.png" alt="Image with text 'this is an official CDC health advisory."></div></figure>
